steps.name: I skip linking my card
I return to the "Home Screen"
I accept Updated Terms and Conditions
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "PAY BY PLATE" tab
I check that the "Manage Pay by Plate" is displayed
I click on "Add Vehicle" button
I click on "COUNTRY" selector
I click on "LITHUANIA" country button
I enter the licence plate "LT29GFTA" in the input
I click on "Add VEHICLE" button
I check that the "Vehicle successfully added" toast message is displayed
I click on "BACK" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "PAY BY PLATE" tab
I check that the "Manage Pay by Plate" is displayed
I check that the "LT29GFTA" license plate is display on the list
